-- 02_category_returns.sql
```sql
WITH approved_returns AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT ON (item_id) item_id
    FROM returns
    WHERE status = 'approved'
    ORDER BY item_id, return_date DESC
),
category_item_counts AS (
    SELECT 
        COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
        oi.item_id
    FROM order_items oi
    JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
    LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    COUNT(*) AS total_items_sold,
    COUNT(ar.item_id) AS total_items_returned,
    ROUND(COUNT(ar.item_id)::DECIMAL / COUNT(*), 4) AS return_rate
FROM category_item_counts cic
LEFT JOIN approved_returns ar ON cic.item_id = ar.item_id
GROUP BY category_name
ORDER BY return_rate DESC;
